&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;दिया गया है: &lt;/span&gt;B - A &amp;divide; D &amp;times; C + E = ?&lt;/p&gt;

