&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Thus, Z is S&amp;#39;s maternal grandmother or mother&amp;#39;s&amp;nbsp;mother.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 4&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage13914.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

